import React from 'react'
import { View, Text, Pressable, Image } from 'react-native'

const MealItem = ({title, imageUrl}) => {
  return (
    <View>
      <Pressable>
        <View>
           <Image source={{uri : imageUrl}}/>
        </View>
        <View>
           <Text>{title}</Text>
        </View>
      </Pressable>
    </View>
  )
}

export default MealItem
